---
// Simple skills table section tailored for Jessica
---
<section id="skills" class="py-12 md:py-16" data-aos="fade" data-aos-duration="300">
  <div class="container space-y-10">
    <h2 class="text-h1-sm md:text-h1 text-center">Skills Matrix</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full min-w-[640px] border-separate border-spacing-0 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <thead class="bg-theme-light">
          <tr>
            <th class="text-start px-4 py-4">Category</th>
            <th class="text-start px-4 py-4">Proficiency</th>
            <th class="text-start px-4 py-4">Years</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-border-light">
          <tr class="even:bg-[#111827] even:text-light"><td class="px-4 py-4">Technical SEO Audits</td><td class="px-4 py-4">Expert</td><td class="px-4 py-4">8+</td></tr>
          <tr class="even:bg-[#111827] even:text-light"><td class="px-4 py-4">GSC & Log Analysis</td><td class="px-4 py-4">Expert</td><td class="px-4 py-4">8+</td></tr>
          <tr class="even:bg-[#111827] even:text-light"><td class="px-4 py-4">Schema / EEAT</td><td class="px-4 py-4">Expert</td><td class="px-4 py-4">5+</td></tr>
          <tr class="even:bg-[#111827] even:text-light"><td class="px-4 py-4">Index Management</td><td class="px-4 py-4">Expert</td><td class="px-4 py-4">6+</td></tr>
          <tr class="even:bg-[#111827] even:text-light"><td class="px-4 py-4">CWV Diagnostics</td><td class="px-4 py-4">Advanced</td><td class="px-4 py-4">4+</td></tr>
          <tr class="even:bg-[#111827] even:text-light"><td class="px-4 py-4">WP Technical SEO</td><td class="px-4 py-4">Expert</td><td class="px-4 py-4">7+</td></tr>
          <tr class="even:bg-[#111827] even:text-light"><td class="px-4 py-4">Dev Collaboration</td><td class="px-4 py-4">Advanced</td><td class="px-4 py-4">5+</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h3 class="mt-8 md:mt-8 text-center text-[24px] font-bold">Key Technical Wins</h3>
    <ul class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-[672px] list-disc space-y-2 text-[14px] leading-[1.6] text-[#111827] pl-6">
      <li>Diagnosed index bloat on 15 enterprise sites</li>
      <li>Recovered 2M+ pages from Google’s supplemental index</li>
      <li>Increased crawl efficiency by 340% via XML sitemap optimization</li>
      <li>Identified and documented CWV issues across 20+ client sites</li>
      <li>Monitored post‑implementation improvements, achieving “Good” scores</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
</section>
